            "id": 6433560,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 富世達(6805)股價拉至漲停，漲停價2105.0元，成交3,458張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富世達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6805:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6805\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6805-TW</a>)27日13:18上漲190元，股價漲停報2105.0元，委買4張、委賣152張，成交3,458張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為3C電子產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富世達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6805:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6805\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6805-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲2.41%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.78%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-255 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+633 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-921 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+33 張</li> <li>融資增減：+306 張</li> <li>融券增減：+19 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
